Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Ponyville\Nis next up for winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing awesome,\Neverypony! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We need those leaves\Noff those trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get autumn cleared\Naway, it'll be "Hello, Winter!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a yawn\NI just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be tired when the\Nmost exciting time of the year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is right around the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget\Nthe best part...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our first winter together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once those ponies bring in\Nthe big fat clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,full of snowflakes, we'll\Nhave a ton of snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for our extreme sledding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And over there we can\Nplay horse hockey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With no shoulder or rump pads!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's looking\Ngreat, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everything. Does\NTank look all right to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he does seem to be\Nmoving a little slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And he looks kind\Nof sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,just like he always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, heh-heh, I'm\Nsure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular Subtitles by YayPonies\NWe have Muffins\Nhttp://main.yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose his heartbeat\NCOULD be a teensy, weensy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,eensy bit slower than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so give him a\Nvitamin or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he\Nneeds that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're just\Nstaying up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many Derring-Do stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's wrong\Nwith him then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. He's\Nperfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just going\Nto hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize he's\Nnot a bear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When the weather grows cold\Nand less food is available,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,many animals hibernate\Nto conserve energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like taking a really\Nlong nap during winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they wake\Nup in spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And see? Even\Ntortoises do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, Tank will\Nleave and dig into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, he'll\Nreappear when the spring sun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,warms the ground back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Tortoises\Ndon't hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony put that picture\Nin there as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then your\Nbook must be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, Tank\Nneeds to hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's healthy for him, just like\Nsleeping is healthy for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, OK, thanks.\NCome on, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To get a second opinion from\Na REAL reptile expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, Rainbow\NDash. I'm a DRAGON!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're\Npractically twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't have to\Nhibernate, why should Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's a TORTOISE.\NAnd I'm a DRAGON.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Same family though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, if Fluttershy says\Ntortoises hibernate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then I guarantee\Ntortoises hiber--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what would you know?\NYou're a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony knows you like\NI do, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need is some hard work\Nto get the ol' blood pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These things are heavy!\NChock full o' snowflakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have such a\Nkiller time in the snow, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank? TANK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, look at that\Ncute wittle Tanky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All snuggly wuggly,\Ngetting ready to hibern---
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,DON'T SAY THAT WORD!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one? Snuggly?\NWuggly? Tanky? Hiberna--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT ONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just saying\Nhow cute he loo--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think hiber-- you know,\Nthat napping thing--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is SOOO cute, why\Ndon't you go do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere far away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie and I are just\Nhaving a conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Rainbow Dash, we all\Nknow how upset you are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,about Tank hiber--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,SHHHH! Don't say that word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what started this all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We know how upset\Nyou are about Tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but you shouldn't take your\Nanger out on your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,WHO SAID ANYTHING ABOUT ANGER?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T SAY\NANYTHING ABOUT ANGER!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT UPSET!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,AND I AM NOT ANGRY!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,DO I LOOK ANGRY?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,C'MON TANK, LET'S\NGET OUTTA HERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you bright-eyed\Nand bushy-tailed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,not sleepy-eyed\Nand scaly-tailed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...which is\Nexactly what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But get up anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You CAN'T hiber--you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about all the primo things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna do\Ntogether this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Building snowponies,\Nstarting snowball fights,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,sipping hot cider by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,DON'T YOU WANT TO DO\NTHOSE THINGS WITH ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Think, Rainbow Dash, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank's only hibernating\Nbecause it's cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd rather have\Nhim awake in the heat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,than asleep in the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to STOP WINTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where do\Nthese clouds go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Over by Clear Skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's Clear\NSkies everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Clear Skies\Nright here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's Clear\NSkies over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Open Skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's open\Nskies everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not everywhere;\NI'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so, you're Open Skies,\Nand you're Clear Skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then what's all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Open, Clear Skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where'd our\Nfluffy clouds go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluffy Clouds?\NHe's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Stopping winter is\Ngonna be a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ When life gives you lemons ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You can make lemonade ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But life gave me Tank, here ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And my choice has{\i0}\N{\i1} long been made. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ No winter will come to{\i0}\N{\i1} Ponyville ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll do it on my own ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I will keep you by my side ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So I will not be alone! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And I'll fly, and I'll fly{\i0}\N{\i1} until the end of the sky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So I'll be the one who{\i0}\N{\i1} doesn't have to say goodbye! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll clear the skies forever{\i0}\N{\i1} So we won't be apart ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll keep the{\i0}\N{\i1} weather warm for you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the winter will{\i0}\N{\i1} never start! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Weather makers, Pegasi ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You make the seasons{\i0}\N{\i1} in the sky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I don't wanna sabotage you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But you see I've got to try! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ No winter can come here now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll keep the warmth{\i0}\N{\i1} and the sun somehow ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'm sorry ponies{\i0}\N{\i1} this has to be ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ For I need my friend{\i0}\N{\i1} and he needs me ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I know it's wrong but{\i0}\N{\i1} what does it matter? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Cause nothing's{\i0}\N{\i1} gonna stop me now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll change it all{\i0}\N{\i1} it's only the weather! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And nopony's gonna{\i0}\N{\i1} bring me down! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll keep the{\i0}\N{\i1} sunlight shining free ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And I'll bust the{\i0}\N{\i1} clouds apart ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ so you can stay with me! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And I'll fly, and I'll fly{\i0}\N{\i1} until the end of the sky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So I'll be the one who{\i0}\N{\i1} doesn't have to say goodbye! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll clear the skies forever{\i0}\N{\i1} So we won't be apart ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'll keep the{\i0}\N{\i1} weather warm for you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the winter will{\i0}\N{\i1} never start! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the next shipment!\NMove those clouds over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For every hoofstep back, they\Ngo three hoofsteps forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale...THAT'S IT, TANK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't stop\Nwinter in Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I can stop\Nit at the source!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch hour! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The winter lab!\NWe're in, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we just gotta figure\Nout a way to shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabotage snowflakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we gotta go\Nbigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. We could get\Nrid of these clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's still\Nnot big enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Slam dunk! With no water, they\Ncan't make clouds or snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't make WINTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to do this to\Nthose weather ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but desperate times call\Nfor desperate measures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie! Looks like these\Nwere a little loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And there goes\Nwinter...down the drain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the name of\NCelestia's goin' on up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves, everypony...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,EVERYPONY! LOOK OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You OK, Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Are\Nyou all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock, knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling,\NRainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor thing\Nlooks so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are we\Ngoing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat we CAN do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Buck up, sugarcube, you just\Nain't yourself these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how can I say\Nthis tactfully?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost your\Nsparkle, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this...but well...\Nyou've become...a party pooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?\NI said whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're here\Nto cheer me up or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, your winter\Nis going to be PETLESS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever did you\Ndo that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she'll never get past\Nthis until she lets it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's OK! Tank'll come\Nback in a few months!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,MONTHS? [wailing]\NI DON'T WANT HIM TO GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.\NThere there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice goin', Fluttershy.\NHow do we get her to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to be about done now.\NCan't be too much left in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor,\Npoor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to see\NFluttershy cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...just...heart-wrenching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everypony, I know how\Nhard it is to say goodbye--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mostly sad because\Nyou're NOT sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Me? What\Nabout Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack cries on\Nthe inside, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Fluttershy.\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she's done or\Njust gettin' a third wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Rainbow\NDash? Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel better.\NReally, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everypony. I don't\Nknow what I'd do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tank. I'm sure\Ngonna miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess we're starting\Nwinter with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The fun's come early! Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we could mess\Nup winter every year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way less work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't think Rainbow\NDash could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding that entire\Nseason from Cloudsdale
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to Ponyville WAS\Npretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you guys might\Nlike to say goodbye to Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's ready to hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using the word!\NShe's using the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when Tank\Nfinishes hibernating,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw him the\Nbiggest Welcome Home party ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or wait. Should it be a\N"Welcome Above Ground" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a "Happy Wake-Up" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe an "It's\Nabout time" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll design him a\Nvery special suit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,just for the occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whichever one it\Nends up being!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're feelin' a\Nlittle better, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you really want to do\Nthis hibernating thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good\Nsleep, Tank!\NSee you later,\Nlittle fella!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Tank,\Nwe'll miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Ready for\Nsome winter fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm gonna hang here\Nand read to him a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That little guy can never get to\Nsleep without a bedtime story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
